items.name: Object_DomainContainer
items.content:
# ===================================================================
#
#   Script: Object_DomainContainer
#
#   $$COPYRIGHT$$
#
# ===================================================================
class Object_DomainContainer extends gs.Object_Base
    ###*
    * A game object which can contain other game objects by domain.
    *
    * @module gs
    * @class Object_DomainContainer
    * @extends gs.Object_Base
    * @memberof gs
    * @constructor
    ###
    constructor: (disposeBehavior) ->
        super
    
        ###*
        * All sub-objects by domain. The default domain is an empty string.
        * @property subObjectsByDomain
        * @type Object
        ###
        @subObjectsByDomain = { "com.degica.vnm.default": @subObjects }
        
        ###*
        * The container's behavior component.
        * @property behavior
        * @type gs.Component_DomainContainer
        ###
        @behavior = new gs.Component_DomainContainer(disposeBehavior)
    
        @addComponent(@behavior)
        
gs.Object_DomainContainer = Object_DomainContainer
